2. No Data Sharing
We do not share, sell, or transfer any of your information to third parties. Your selections and preferences are saved locally on your device and are not transmitted anywhere.

3. Notifications
FitWithEase may send you reminder notifications to encourage regular exercise. You can control these notifications from your device settings at any time.

4. Crash Reports and Analytics
To improve app performance and stability, we may use third-party services like Google Firebase Crashlytics to collect anonymous crash logs. These reports do not contain personally identifiable information.

5. Permissions
